{"tid":1058430,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得油塘站要改名做鯉魚門站","createTime":"2019-03-12T13:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T08:01:57.000Z","uid":123613,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e073955cd66391ff9c2ab77a2c63a5f71e55dfa7","tid":1058430,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"論名氣，鯉魚門一定大過油塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 油塘站附近又有條鯉魚門道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算講好聽好意頭，鯉魚門一定好過油塘，油塘讀音咁似留堂，學生一定唔like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n計我話，如果油塘站改做鯉魚門，咁就皆大歡喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbabe37d07a6bfa73f423b81f83d2936c198bda","tid":1058430,"uid":123613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9efcc412aca9563a57b9d9ed8ab3d0cf2f0e77b","tid":1058430,"uid":125731,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:10:58.000Z","msg":"叫大本營站丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92398cef32ee3866113adaf835998e12c501bb5","tid":1058430,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b9efcc412aca9563a57b9d9ed8ab3d0cf2f0e77b","tid":1058430,"uid":125731,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:10:58.000Z","msg":"叫大本營站丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"大本型冇鯉魚門咁多人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大本型=商場名<br />\n油塘=屋邨名<br />\n鯉魚門=屋邨名+商場名+主要馬路名+旅遊區<br />\n<br />\n油塘站改做鯉魚門其實好合理喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6248fa682e4986da22b11fbfa5b6b77822dc95","tid":1058430,"uid":38651,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e92398cef32